RayChess PS3
============

This project is a PlayStation 3 port of ray-chess and is distributed under the
MIT License (see LICENSE).

Original work
-------------
ray-chess — https://github.com/GustavoHenriqueMuller/ray-chess
Copyright (c) 2023 Gustavo Henrique Müller.
Licensed under the MIT License.

The chess engine (board, pieces, move generation, rules, rendering) is reused
essentially verbatim from ray-chess. Only the platform I/O layer was rewritten
for the PS3:
  - source/Game.cpp        : window at the PS3 output resolution, a Camera2D that
                             centers the board, gamepad quit, and asset loading
                             from embedded memory instead of std::filesystem.
  - data/*.png, data/*.bin : the piece sprites, move indicators, and click/cancel
                             sounds taken verbatim from ray-chess's assets/.

